sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Frontend as Frontend Interface
    participant Backend as Backend Server
    participant DB as Database

    User->>Frontend: Opens the application
    User->>Frontend: Logs into the system
    Frontend->>Backend: Sends login request
    Backend->>Backend: Validates user credentials
    Backend->>DB: Queries the database
    DB-->>Backend: Returns user data
    Backend-->>Frontend: Sends response
    User->>Frontend: Accesses dashboard
    User->>Frontend: Performs main system action
    Frontend->>Backend: Forwards user action
    Backend->>DB: Processes request and updates database
    DB-->>Backend: Confirms update
    Backend-->>Frontend: Returns success/status
    Frontend-->>User: Updates UI
